Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:17.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}誰が決めたんだ　そんな生き方らしくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.89,0:01:23.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}やりたいこと貫く力　それこそが強さだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:27.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}分かっているから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.02,0:01:29.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I believe in what I've done
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:36.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}歩んできた日々を　懐かしむ意味を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}I'm struggling now to overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:45.37,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}諦めることはない　最後まで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:47.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Get down, let's get down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:54.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}心の光を　覚えてるうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:58.68,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Trust yourself. Don't be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:03.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Save yourself. Don't forget.
