Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}No reason to go back again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:36.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}我會回憶走過的路 找出價值所在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.65,0:01:38.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\be5\fad(150,150)}Easy losing memories
